OM/RCM Comparison

Apical F comparison between the OM and RCM.

Difference in apical F between the OM and RCM. Positive values indicate higher F in the OM.

SSB comparison between the OM and RCM.

Difference in spawning biomass (SSB), relative to SSB0, between the OM and RCM, calculated as \((SSB^{OM}_y - SSB^{RCM}_y)/SSB^{OM}_0\). Positive values indicate higher SSB in the OM.

Recruitment comparison between the OM and RCM.

Difference in recruitment (relative to R0) between the OM and RCM, calculated as \((R^{OM}_y - R^{RCM}_y)/R^{OM}_0\). Positive values indicate higher recruitment in the OM.

Comparison of total removals between the OM and RCM.

Difference in removals (relative to RCM predicted), calculated as \(C^{OM}_y/C^{RCM}_y - 1\). Positive values indicate higher removals in the OM.
